        <h1>CapuccinoExpress: Travel Agency</h1>
        <p class="first_thing">Having struggle to choose where to travel? <strong> We can help with that</strong>.</p>
        <h2>Where to travel</h2>
        <p>Many people wonder where they can go on holiday, and for <em>many</em> reasons as well. "<em>Oh, honey I want to go to a beach-like place!"</em>, then <em>"But darling, I want to go to a forest-like place!"</em>. It happens <strong>all</strong>the time.</p>
    <p>Here we have some <strong>dream-like </strong>places that might be the solution to <em>that</em> kind of problems.</p> <ul>
        <li>Santorini, Greece</li>
        <li>Banff & Moraine Lake, Canada</li>
        <li>Lapland, Finland</li>
    </ul>
    <h3>Santorini, Greece</h3>
    <img src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/e/e4/Santorini_Montage_L.png/500px-Santorini_Montage_L.png" alt="Santorini, Greece" width="220">
    <p>This is a wonderful, dream-like place, it has Whitewashed buildings, blue domes, cliffside views over a deep blue caldera. </p>
    <h3>Banff & Moraine Lake, Canada</h3>
    <img src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/c/c5/Moraine_Lake_17092005.jpg/1280px-Moraine_Lake_17092005.jpg" alt="Banff & Moraine Lake, Canada" width="220">
    <ol><li>Turquoise lakes</li>
        <li>towering snow-capped peaks</li>
        <li>untouched alpine forests</li></ol><p>Those are both the top 3 best things a dream-like place should have, and top 3 best things <strong>Moraine Lake</strong> have.</p> <h3>Lapland, Finland</h3><img src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/3/34/Arctic_circle_santa_village.jpg" alt="Lapland, Finland" width="220"> <p>A winter wonderland of snow-covered forests, reindeer, the northern lights, and glass igloos where you can watch the aurora from bed.</p>
        <p>-</p>
        <p>We hope you liked our selection of places to visit this holidays. See you! </p>
    
